# INSTALL

for local develop

```
docker run -d --name psql-server  -p 5432:5432 -v $PWD/db/psql:/var/lib/postgresql/data postgres
docker run -it --rm --link psql-server:postgres postgres psql -h postgres -Upostgres
```

heroku deploy

```
# initial
heroku create
heroku addons:create heroku-postgresql:hobby-dev
```

```
# masterブランチじゃないとデプロイできない
git add -A
git commit -m ''
git push heroku master
heroku run rake db:migrate
```
